   <narrative xml:lang="EN">INSO Nigeria 2018</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">North Eastern Nigeria remains the most impacted geographical area by the current armed conflict in the Lake Chad Basin region. INSO Nigeria provides registered NGOs operating in the area with safety and security services that improve their situational awareness, provide an evidence base for operational practice and support safe humanitarian access. Services include round the clock alerts and information, analysis, incident mapping, crises assistance, coordination meetings and a comprehensive portfolio of training and capacity building services. INSO has been serving NGOs in North Eastern Nigeria since 2016.</narrative>
  </description>
